@title: File coherence
@description: A source file must match a logical entity, and group all the
functions associated with that entity. Grouping functions that are not related
to each other in the same file has to be avoided
@warning: Beyond 5 functions in your file, you must subdivide your logical entity
into several sub-entities.
entities.
@severity: 3
@check: 1
@file_type: *.c *.h
